{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)-3lhdz","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to write "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" bytes from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"text":" into the stream. Will block","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"during the operation."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"write"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"CancellableT"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableT"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableT"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableProtocol","text":"CancellableProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19CancellableProtocolP"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is 0, returns 0 and does nothing. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"larger than ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" is 0).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancelled"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is set accordingly.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"write","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"CancellableT"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableT"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE5write6buffer5count11cancellableSiSvSg_Siqd__SgtKAA011CancellableD0Rd__lF","title":"write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)-3lhdz"]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStreamProtocol/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)-3lhdz":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)-3lhdz","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Tries to write ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" bytes from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"text":" into the stream. Will block","t